Package: sdtt
Type: Package
Title: Simple Detection Theory Tool
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
  person(
  given = "Stuart B.",
  family = "Moore",
  role = c("aut", "cre"),
  email = "s.b.moore@keele.ac.uk",
  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0747-9304")
  )
Maintainer: Stuart B. Moore <s.b.moore@keele.ac.uk>
Description: A simple detection theory tool for calculating detection theory statistics.
  Assign conditional probabilities per participant, per condition and calculate proportion
  of each conditional probability. Raw totals for each conditional probability can also be
  requested by the user. 
Depends:
  dplyr
Imports:
  dplyr
